Package org.gvsig.fmap.dal.coverage.grid Description

A grid is a class which represents a set of cells.

Through this object the user can apply kernel operations to a set of cells contained in a Buffer. Other basic operations to data access can be used but it is advisable to use the Buffer class for those operations.
